[SN]TITLE[SN]
Sadio Mane: Liverpool forward suffers muscle injury in training

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Liverpool forward Sadio Mane is a doubt for Saturday's Premier League match at Burnley after suffering a muscle injury in training.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 24-year-old suffered the problem during a morning session at Melwood.
Some earlier reports on Wednesday had suggested the Senegal international might have dislocated his shoulder.
